All Classes

Class Description
AnalyticsCounter
AnalyticsCounter is a class organizing the symptoms felt by the patient into a comprehensive and ordered frequency list Each symptom is : Retrieved from an original txt file Counted (number of occurrences) Listed alphabetically All listed symptoms together with their number of occurrences are exported to an output file.
IOccurrenceWriter
Anything that will write symptoms in an output.
ISymptomReader
Anything that will read symptom data from a source The important part is, the return value from the operation, which is a list of strings, that may contain many duplications The implementation does not need to order the list
ReadSymptomDataFromFile
Reads symptom data from a file The return value is a list of strings (symptoms) with some possible duplicates.
SymptomFrequencyCounter
Parameter given is a list of strings (symptoms), may contain duplicates Creates a set of string from initial list containing once every symptom retrieved: no duplicates.
WriteSymptomCountInFile
Creates an output file containing symptoms and their respective count, ordered alphabetically One symptom-count pair per line.
